text: CLIF may refer to: * Common Logic Interchange Format, a dialect of the Common Logic Standard * Courage, Loyalty, Integrity, Fairness (abbreviated C.L.I.F.), a police procedural series produced in Singapore ** It may also refer to one of the other five seasons: C.L.I.F. 2, C.L.I.F. 3, C.L.I.F. 4, or C.L.I.F. 5 * Clif Bar, an American company that produces organic foods and drinks
title: CLIF
